optimize_dataset.py

Optimizes a pandas DataFrame for analytics by:

- Converting object/string columns to category dtype
- Standardizing numeric columns (z-score normalization by default, or min-max)
- Printing a before/after memory usage summary

Usage:
from optimize_dataset import optimize_dataset
df_optimized, report = optimize_dataset(df)

```
